There are two types of cursor:
1.) Implicit 
2.) Explicit

Basic Syntax of Explicit Cursor:
DECLARE

    CURSOR emp_cursor IS
        SELECT name
        FROM employees;

    emp_name VARCHAR2(30);

BEGIN

    OPEN emp_cursor;

    FETCH emp_cursor INTO emp_name;

    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE(emp_name);

    CLOSE emp_cursor;

END;
/
